    <item>
      <title>中国批准1978年以来首次延长退休年龄方案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/china-approves-plan-for-first-hike-to-retirement-age-since-1978</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国将自1978年以来首次提高退休年龄，此举可能会减缓劳动力的下降，但却会激怒那些已经饱受经济放缓困扰的工人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/china-approves-plan-for-first-hike-to-retirement-age-since-1978</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Sep 2024 06:34:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>藐视南非领导人祖马的普拉温·戈尔丹去世</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/pravin-gordhan-who-defied-south-african-leader-zuma-dies-at-75</link>
      <description><![CDATA[普拉温·戈尔丹 (Pravin Gordhan) 去世，享年 75 岁。他曾担任南非内阁的三个职位，并在雅各布·祖马 (Jacob Zuma) 丑闻缠身的总统任期内敢于反抗，赢得了赞誉。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/pravin-gordhan-who-defied-south-african-leader-zuma-dies-at-75</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Sep 2024 04:16:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
