      <title>俄罗斯黑客突然袭击台湾证券交易所和银行</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/hackers-hit-taiwan-bourse-major-bank-in-mystery-foreign-attack</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯黑客组织短暂破坏了台湾的金融平台，包括证券交易所和兆丰金控的网站，暴露了台湾容易受到外国网络攻击的弱点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/hackers-hit-taiwan-bourse-major-bank-in-mystery-foreign-attack</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Sep 2024 02:59:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟国家将就与俄罗斯的新接触向 IMF 总裁提出质询</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/eu-nations-to-question-imf-chief-over-new-russia-engagement</link>
      <description><![CDATA[几个欧盟国家打算向国际货币基金组织总裁克里斯塔利娜·格奥尔基耶娃提出质疑，因为这家总部位于华盛顿的银行计划自乌克兰入侵以来首次与俄罗斯就经济问题进行接触。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/eu-nations-to-question-imf-chief-over-new-russia-engagement</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 18:14:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
